modules.description: Handles C-stub compilation and OPAM package configuration for GTK bindings, managing dependencies and build processes. Works with Dune build files, OPAM metadata, and C library interfaces. Ensures reproducible builds by isolating C libraries into distinct packages.

Provides functions to compute rendering dimensions for SVGs, including size constraints based on fixed dimensions, zoom factors, and maximum size limits. Operates on integers, floats, and a callback type `size_fun` that maps dimensions to a scaled output. Used to render SVG content from strings or files with specified DPI and layout adjustments.
